_sText:
The v4 version have been corrupted for some servers, and I decided to make a new one.

The new "The One" feature:
When you catch the "The One" secret, the next traps that teleport you to the Noob Box will teleport you back to the Secure Room in office area due the new powers ! 4 traps will remain when you catch the "The One" secret.

Final words:
Please download, test it, leave a constructive feedback and rate !

Hope you like it !
